A Maximal transport pod arrives on the scene, coming in low so 
scanners don't pick it up too soon. A grey wolf jumps out as it's 
moving.

"Lunarpine Maximize" he yells as his feet touch the ground. Drawing 
his rifle and ducking behind a nearby rock formation. 

"Lunarpine to Maximals, whats the status?" a propper way of asking 
who should I hit. The battle was joined and the slagging could begin. 
LUNARPINE HAS ARRIVED.
